---
const siteTitle = "il Blog di Lujanta";

// Cambia questo percorso se il file ha un nome diverso
const coverImage = "/cover.jpg";

// Didascalia in alto a destra (come nel tuo esempio)
const coverCaptionLine1 = "Pragser Wildsee —";
const coverCaptionLine2 = "Lago di Braies";
const coverCaptionLine3 = "archivio personale";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="it">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
    <title>{siteTitle}</title>

    <style>
      :root{
        --bg:#f4f1ea;
        --paper:#eee8de;
        --ink:#2b2a26;
        --muted:#5a564d;
        --line:#d6cfbf;
        --accent:#8b6f4e; /* rame spento */
      }

      *{ box-sizing:border-box; }
      body{
        margin:0;
        background:var(--bg);
        color:var(--ink);
        font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
        line-height:1.7;
      }

      .wrap{
        max-width: 980px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 48px 18px 80px;
      }

      /* HERO */
      .hero{
        text-align:center;
        padding-top: 10px;
      }

      .cover{
        position:relative;
        display:block;
        width: min(920px, 100%);
        margin: 0 auto 26px;
        background: var(--paper);
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
        padding: 12px;
      }

      /* Se vuoi un effetto “pergamena erosa” leggero senza immagini extra */
      .cover::before{
        content:"";
        position:absolute;
        inset: 6px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(139,111,78,.18);
        pointer-events:none;
      }

      .cover img{
        display:block;
        width:100%;
        height:auto;
        border-radius: 2px;
      }

      .cover-caption{
        position:absolute;
        right: 26px;
        bottom: 86px; /* tarato per stare “a lato” come nel tuo mock */
        text-align:right;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.25;
        font-style: italic;
        text-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(244,241,234,.85);
      }
      .cover-caption strong{
        font-style: normal;
        font-weight: normal;
        letter-spacing: .02em;
      }

      h1{
        margin: 6px 0 8px;
        font-size: 46px;
        font-weight: normal;
        letter-spacing: .02em;
      }

      .subtitle{
        margin: 0 auto 18px;
        max-width: 760px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 18px;
      }

      .cap-words{
        text-transform: uppercase;   /* MAIUSCOLO */
        font-weight: normal;         /* NON grassetto */
        letter-spacing: .05em;
        color: var(--ink);
      }

      .cap-one{
        text-transform: uppercase;   /* CULTURE in maiuscolo */
        font-weight: normal;
        letter-spacing: .04em;
        color: var(--ink);
      }

      .btn{
        display:inline-block;
        margin-top: 10px;
        padding: 10px 22px;
        border: 1px solid var(--accent);
        background: transparent;
        color: var(--ink);
        text-decoration:none;
        letter-spacing:.06em;
      }
      .btn:hover{
        background: rgba(139,111,78,.07);
      }

      .orn{
        margin: 26px auto 34px;
        width: min(560px, 95%);
        height: 1px;
        background: var(--line);
        position: relative;
      }
      .orn::after{
        content:"✦";
        position:absolute;
        left:50%;
        transform:translateX(-50%);
        top:-14px;
        background: var(--bg);
        padding: 0 10px;
        color: var(--accent);
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      /* SEZIONI */
      .section-title{
        font-size: 40px;
        margin: 10px 0 18px;
        font-weight: normal;
      }

      .cards{
        display:grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
        gap: 18px;
        margin-bottom: 36px;
      }

      .card{
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        background: rgba(255,255,255,.18);
        padding: 18px 18px 20px;
        text-align:left;
        position:relative;
        min-height: 110px;
      }
      .card h3{
        margin: 0 0 8px;
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: normal;
      }
      .card p{
        margin:0;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 16px;
      }
      .arrow{
        position:absolute;
        right:14px;
        bottom:12px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 22px;
      }

      .path{
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        background: rgba(255,255,255,.18);
        padding: 18px;
        text-align:left;
        position:relative;
      }
      .path h3{
        margin: 0 0 8px;
        font-size: 26px;
        font-weight: normal;
      }
      .path p{
        margin: 0 0 12px;
        color: var(--muted);
      }
      .mini-btn{
        display:inline-block;
        border:1px solid var(--line);
        padding: 6px 12px;
        text-decoration:none;
        color: var(--ink);
        font-size: 14px;
        background: transparent;
      }

      .footer-note{
        margin-top: 26px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 16px;
        text-align:center;
        max-width: 760px;
        margin-left:auto;
        margin-right:auto;
      }

      @media (max-width: 520px){
        h1{ font-size: 36px; }
        .section-title{ font-size: 32px; }
        .cover-caption{ right: 18px; bottom: 74px; font-size: 13px; }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <main class="wrap">
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="cover">
          <img src={coverImage} alt="Copertina: paesaggio innevato del lago" />

          <div class="cover-caption" aria-label="Didascalia immagine">
            <strong>{coverCaptionLine1}</strong><br />
            <strong>{coverCaptionLine2}</strong><br />
            {coverCaptionLine3}
          </div>
        </div>

        <h1>{siteTitle}</h1>

        <p class="subtitle">
          <span class="cap-words">Tradizioni, Folklore e Stregoneria</span><br />
          nelle <span class="cap-one">Culture</span> alpine e nei loro intrecci europei nel tempo
        </p>

        <a class="btn" href="/inizia-da-qui">Inizia da qui</a>

        <div class="orn"></div>

        <h2 class="section-title">Scoperte consigliate</h2>

        <div class="cards">
          <a class="card" href="https://ilblogdilujanta.blogspot.com/2025/12/la-smara-e-i-molti-nomi-della-trude.html" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
            <h3>La Šmara e i molti nomi della Trude</h3>
            <p>Figure femminili dell’inverno e del confine.</p>
            <span class="arrow">→</span>
          </a>

          <a class="card" href="https://ilblogdilujanta.blogspot.com/2016/12/krampus-e-perchten-gli-oscuri-spiriti.html" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
            <h3>Krampus e Perchten</h3>
            <p>Gli oscuri spiriti delle tradizioni alpine.</p>
            <span class="arrow">→</span>
          </a>

          <a class="card" href="https://ilblogdilujanta.blogspot.com/2016/03/trumusiate-sainate-la-divinita-del.html" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
            <h3>Trumusiate Sainate</h3>
            <p>La divinità del bosco e dei margini.</p>
            <span class="arrow">→</span>
          </a>
        </div>

        <h2 class="section-title">Percorsi di lettura</h2>

        <div class="path">
          <h3>Spiriti, miti e tradizioni d’inverno</h3>
          <p>Figure notturne, rituali stagionali e simboli tra luce e buio.</p>
          <a class="mini-btn" href="#">Scopri il percorso</a>
          <span class="arrow">→</span>
        </div>

        <p class="footer-note">
          Puoi seguire i percorsi proposti, esplorare per temi o luoghi, oppure iniziare da un singolo articolo.
        </p>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
